1
00:00:01,960 --> 00:00:04,630
Okay, we're rolling.

2
00:00:05,130 --> 00:00:06,260
So...

3
00:00:06,260 --> 00:00:09,220
Please tell us what inspired you
to do this job.

4
00:00:11,260 --> 00:00:14,180
What... what inspired me?

5
00:00:15,140 --> 00:00:17,230
Well...

6
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:29,700
I wanted to help someone

7
00:00:30,030 --> 00:00:33,030
become the school festival prince.

8
00:00:39,830 --> 00:00:44,540
Whew, I was so nervous!

9
00:00:45,050 --> 00:00:46,710
You did really well.

10
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:49,670
But you're clenching your hands so tightly.

11
00:00:50,340 --> 00:00:51,930
Does it hurt?

12
00:00:51,930 --> 00:00:53,340
No, I'm fine.

13
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:55,430
Really? Let me see.

14
00:00:55,510 --> 00:00:57,810
I'm fine, see?

15
00:00:58,810 --> 00:01:00,770
Looking into your eyes while talking

16
00:01:01,060 --> 00:01:02,720
seems to make me less nervous.

17
00:01:03,730 --> 00:01:04,860
Thank you.

18
00:01:04,860 --> 00:01:08,940
Being this close at work
feels a bit strange.

19
00:01:08,940 --> 00:01:10,780
Oh...

20
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:16,450
How so?
